      • expandGroup

        PanelMenuGroup expandGroup(ChoicePicker picker)
        Expands group which satisfies the rules given in picker object. Note that group need to be enabled and visible before calling this method.
        Parameters:
        picker - object to define which group should be expanded
        Returns:
        the group which was expanded
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if group is not enabled or visible, or does not exist
